name: Tactical-Life.com Upgrade
tagline: Site refresh using Wordpress publishing platform.
body:
### Tactical-Life Site Refresh
The goal of this project is to upgrade the existing Tactical-Life.com website to support the latest web standards. The Wordpress CMS will be upgraded as well.

Check out the current website at www.tactical-life.com
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
